titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3055.
Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3055.

action.text: Mrs. Lowey asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: This concurrent resolution directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3055 (Further Continuing Appropriations Act, 2020, and Further Health Extenders Act of 2019) to (1) amend the title, and (2) make a technical correction to section 1703.
